otherFacts.name: ROOM FEATURES
otherFacts.value: Walk-In Closet, Built-Ins, Prefab Fireplace, Island, Separate Shower

data.description: Don't miss this opportunity to own your own private lake retreat on beautiful Lake Sinclair. This spacious 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home features LVP flooring throughout. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining with a stone accented fireplace and built-in bookcases being a focal point in the family room. The kitchen is what dreams are made of with tile backsplash, farmhouse sink, stainless steel appliances, and a work island with a butcher block countertop. The master retreat includes your own personal oasis with marble countertops, a standalone tub, oversized tile shower which all leads into a custom built walk-in closet including an island. The laundry room with a laundry sink is conveniently located next to the master closest making laundry an ease. The remaining 3 bedrooms are located on the opposite side of the home, one of which has a private bathroom attached. Walk out onto your sprawling front porch and just relax or enjoy views of the lake. Come see this home today.
